        the basics of the editor, nodes, scenes, GDScript, and signals through practical 
        examples. By the end of the series, you’ll have the foundations you need to 
        confidently start creating games in Xogot.
        
        @TutorialReference(tutorial: "doc:1_nodes_and_scenes")
        @TutorialReference(tutorial: "doc:2_instancing")
        @TutorialReference(tutorial: "doc:4_scripting_first_script")
        @TutorialReference(tutorial: "doc:5_scripting_player_input")
        @TutorialReference(tutorial: "doc:6_signals")
    }
    @Chapter(name: "Your First 2D Game") {
        @Image(source: dodge_preview.gif)
        
